  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion testable="true">`SessionSummarizeOrchestrator` resolves playbook via `_consumerRouting.ResolveAsync("chat-summarize")`; FR-26 / FR-30 invariants preserved.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">`AppOnlyAnalysisService` resolves playbook via `_consumerRouting.ResolveAsync("email-analysis")`; 2 const stable-IDs at `:46` and `:1068` (per task 027 evidence) removed.</criterion>
