  <notes>
    Parallel-safe with 028c — separate consumer files. The 2 const sites at `AppOnlyAnalysisService.cs:46,1068` were intentionally preserved by Phase 1 task 020 design (documented in task 027 exit-gate evidence) precisely because Phase 1R was the planned removal vehicle. Removing them closes the only remaining hardcoded-GUID gap in the BFF AI execution paths. The `chat-summarize` migration is also the FR-05 lowest-blast-radius consumer per the original Phase 1 prioritization — preserving its behavior verbatim is non-negotiable.
  </notes>

